### Appendix B: NAV Decay Penalty Formula  
NAV Decay Penalty Score = 100 - min(100, max(0, (NAV Decay % - 5) × 20))  
Example: 7% decay → 60 penalty score → 40% reduction in TEYR contribution.

### Appendix C: Sample Quality Warning Flag  
Green: AEY ≥40%, decay ≤5% → Normal operation.  
Yellow: AEY 25–39% or decay 5–10% → Caution, reduced weighting possible.  
Red: AEY <25% or decay >10% → Administrator review required before allocation.

